verses.text:
For their duty was to wait on the sons of Aaron for the service of
the LORD’s house—in the courts, in the rooms, and in the purifying of all holy things, even the work of
the service of God’s house;

for the show bread also, and for the fine flour for a meal offering,
whether of unleavened wafers, or of that which is baked in the pan, or of that which is soaked, and for
all measurements of quantity and size;

and to offer all burnt offerings to the LORD on the Sabbaths, on the
new moons, and on the set feasts, in number according to the ordinance concerning them, continually before
the LORD;
